Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.24,0:21:04.96,Dial-CH,,0,500,0,,唐音好可愛
Dialogue: 1,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.36,Dial-CH,,500,0,0,,喜歡你
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.96,0:21:07.40,Dial-CH,,0,500,0,,好可愛好可愛好可愛
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.36,0:21:09.05,Dial-CH,,500,0,0,,喜歡你喜歡你
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.40,0:21:09.55,Dial-CH,,0,500,0,,最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.05,0:21:09.96,Dial-CH,,500,0,0,,最喜歡你了
