Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.96,0:21:13.25,Dial-CH,,500,0,0,,最喜歡戀太郎了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.89,0:21:12.17,Dial-CH,,0,500,0,,最喜歡你了
